natspec.details: Contract that allows members to vote on various aspects of Cardinal House through a poll

closePoll().details: Only owner function to close the poll and add it to the list of previous polls.

createNewPoll(string,string[]).details: Only owner function to create a new poll for the community.

params.pollTitle: The title of the new poll.
params.proposalNames: String array containing the names of all proposals for the new poll.

getNumberOfProposals().details: Gets the number of proposals in the current poll.

returns.numProposals: the number of proposals in the current poll.

getPastProposal(uint256,uint256).details: Gets a single proposal from a previous poll.

params.pastPollIndex: The index of the previous poll in the pastPolls array.
params.proposalIndex: The index of the proposal in the previous poll's proposal array.

returns.proposal: the proposal from the previous poll.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

vote(uint256).details: Voting function that allows a user to vote in the current poll.

params.proposal: The index of the proposal in the poll's proposal array.

winningProposal().details: Computes the winning proposal taking all previous votes into account.

returns.winningProposal_: index of winning proposal in the proposals array

winningProposalName().details: Calls winningProposal() function to get the index of the winner contained in the proposals array and then
